sources.description:
Refuge: American Apocalypse chronicles the struggles of a family trying to stay alive in the wake of a deadly and catastrophic virus that has brought America to its knees. In what was once a thriving American suburb that has now devolved into a lawless world of roaming gangs and dwindling resources, the family is discovered and forced to fight back in order to survive.
2013.  Stars: Carter Roy, Amy Rutberg, Eva Grace Kellner
